column5: only been out on her once ,, still a bit sore back there , thanks . any ice ? just a walk out . lookin' to even the score.

not sure about ice conditions...There was a small bait shop right on Rama Rd... however the name escapes me.. give them a call if you can remember it...  what are you targeting? and I can give you some tips on locations to fish..  G
Ice is good to go now from airport side. Other side near plant should be a go as well. Ice is getting pretty thick there and making more each day with these temps

pike will be the main focus during daylight,  as the sun sets we'll gear up for some wally's . been to that bait shop but no, can't remember it either . any tips would be great, i'd  appreciate the info
